    <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/ChatGPT-Image-Nov-7-2025-07_51_18-PM.png" alt="Reverse Mortgage vs HELOC: Which Equity Access Tool Is Right for Seniors?" width="1200" height="675" loading="eager" />
